data.description: TAKE A LOOK AT THIS WELCOMING HOME LOCATED ON A LARGE 0.30-ACRE LOT WITH AN RV PAD, 30 AMP SERVICE, CLEAN OUT AND HOSE BIBB. QUAINT COVERED FRONT PORCH, LOW MAINTENANCE LANDSCAPE & NICE CURB APPEAL. THIS 3BD/2BA SPLIT FLOOR PLAN INCLUDES GAS STOVE IN LIVING ROOM WHICH OPENS TO DINING AREA WITH FRENCH DOORS TO THE BACKYARD & COVERED PATIO.  KITCHEN FEATURES BREAKFAST BAR, LOTS OF COUNTER SPACE AND ALL APPLIANCES. THE PRIMARY BEDROOM FEATURES AND EN SUITE BATH AND WALK-IN CLOSET. THE HOME FEATURES CENTRAL AIR/HEATING AND BASEBOARD HEAT. BACKYARD IS LARGE ENOUGH TO BUILD A SHOP OR GARAGE AND HAS DOUBLE GATES ON BOTH SIDES OF THE HOUSE AND INCLUDES A STORAGE SHED. HOME NEEDS YOUR TOUCH. COME CHECK IT OUT!  WELCOME HOME.
